---
// Corporate intro text over marble background
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about__inner container">
    <p class="about__text">
      Magna Cerámica connects the UK market with leading Spanish ceramic tile
      brands through specialized commercial representation and expert industry
      support.
    </p>
    <p class="about__text">
      With an experienced team and a strong network in Spain's ceramic sector,
      Magna is a trusted source for quality products, reliable manufacturers,
      and professional service.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    position: relative;
    background-image: url("/img/corporate-bg.webp");
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about__inner {
    padding-block: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 8rem);
  }

  .about__text {
    max-width: 58rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.9vw, 1.6rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .about__text + .about__text {
    margin-top: 1.5em;
  }

  /* background-attachment: fixed is unreliable on mobile */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about {
      background-attachment: scroll;
    }
  }
</style>
